<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When defining a console route as described here(<a href="http://packages.zendframework.com/docs/latest/manual/en/modules/zend.console.routes.html">http://packages.zendframework.com/docs/latest/…</a>) it's beeing matched by the console router but the defined controllerAction won't be dispatched. the eventmanager triggers dispatch.error and the application prints it's usage information.</p>

